Arthritis Explained: Symptoms and Treatment at Ponjesly Hospital

Arthritis, a condition marked by joint inflammation, can significantly impact daily life. Ponjesly Hospital is committed to offering effective management strategies for arthritis, which can affect anyone regardless of age. Common forms include osteoarthritis and rheumatoid arthritis, presenting symptoms like joint pain, swelling, and reduced mobility.
Effective management of arthritis involves medications to control pain and inflammation, physical therapy to maintain joint function, and sometimes surgery for severe cases. At Ponjesly Hospital, we focus on individualized treatment plans to address each patient's unique needs, aiming to improve their overall well-being and mobility.
Learn more - https://ponjeslyhospital.in/understanding-arthritis/
